<C>__{forrest}
<D>__{which way?}
<C>__{lt. dan}
<D>__{over there! they're over there! get, get on the wheel and take a left!}
<C>__{forrest}
<D>__{okay.}
<C>__{lt. dan}
<D>__{gump, what are you doing? take a left! left! that's where we're gonna find those shrimp, my boy! that's where we'll find 'em.}
<A>__{forrest empties the net. their "catch" is debris that falls to the deck.}
